@startuml sequence_subtitles_v2
title Subtitles v2 - Comedia javni API (gore) + PDF sablon Platforme/HAL ispod Comedije (demonstration)
' Sabloni: Module 3 (DVB subtitle = bitmap, PTS sync), Module 6 Fig.2/3 (platform/HAL),
' Module 7 Fig.3 (Comedia interna arhitektura - "TTX & Sub", TDAL_GFX, TDAL_PTSM)
' Precondition: Zapping use case je vec zavrsen (service started, PAT/PMT vec parsirani),
' liveRoute je validan i subtitle PID je vec poznat iz PMT-a.

actor User
box "Android app" #EBF5FF
  participant "Live TV App" as App
  participant "Broadcast TvInputService" as TIS
end box
box "Comedia - iWedia liba4tv" #E8F5E9
  participant "SubtitleControl" as SUB
  participant "StreamComponentControl" as SC
  participant "DisplayControl" as DISP
  participant "Comedia CHAL - TDAL" as CHAL
end box
box "Ispod Comedije - Platform i HAL - demonstration" #FFF3E0
  participant "Tuner SDK / Demux Filter" as TSDK
  participant "GPU / Display" as GPU
end box

TIS -> SUB : registerListener(subtitleListener)
TIS -> SC : registerListener(streamComponentListener)

SC --> TIS : StreamComponentListener.componentChanged(routeID, StreamComponentType.SUBTITLE)
note over SC,CHAL : Comedia interno: PMT subtitle deskriptor (PID, composition/ancillary page ID) -> CHAL (TDAL)

CHAL -> TSDK : otvori subtitle PID filter
note over TSDK : demonstration: demux PID filter za subtitle PES\nkomunicira sa HAL (DEMUX) (ref. Module 6 Fig.4/5)
TSDK --> CHAL : subtitle PES segmenti

SUB --> TIS : SubtitleListener.updateTrackCount(SubtitleType.DVB, cnt)
TIS -> SUB : getSubtitleTrackCount(routeID)
SUB --> TIS : int cnt
loop za svaku raspoloživu traku
  TIS -> SUB : getSubtitleTrack(routeID, trackIndex)
  SUB --> TIS : SubtitleTrack
end

TIS -> SUB : setSubtitleType(SubtitleType.DVB)
TIS -> SUB : setCurrentSubtitleTrack(routeID, trackIndex)
SUB --> TIS : A4TVStatus
note over SUB : Opciono: setSubtitleMode(SubtitleMode.HEARING_IMPAIRED)\nako PMT nudi varijantu za slušno oštećene/prevod

TIS -> SUB : enableAutomaticSubtitleDisplay(true)
note over SUB : Automatski prikaz je enabled by default.\nEkvivalentan poziv za superimpose track: enableSuperimpose().

TIS -> DISP : setGraficSurface(surfaceBundle)
DISP --> TIS : A4TVStatus
DISP -> CHAL : graphics plane spreman za subtitle bitmap
CHAL -> GPU : dekoduj bitmap segment + PCR/PTS sync; renderuj na graphics plane
note over GPU : demonstration: TDAL_GFX (bitmap render) + TDAL_PTSM (PTS sync)\nkomunicira sa HAL (GPU/Display) (ref. Module 6 Fig.5; Module 3 PCR/PTS)
GPU --> CHAL : bitmap composed preko video plane-a
CHAL --> DISP : subtitle prikazan

TIS -> SUB : getCurrentSubtitleTrackIndex(routeID)
SUB --> TIS : int trackIndex

TIS -> SUB : deselectCurrentSubtitleTrack(routeID)
SUB --> TIS : A4TVStatus

TIS -> SUB : unregisterListener(subtitleListener)
TIS -> SC : unregisterListener(streamComponentListener)
@enduml
